<section id="Section542088">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>sales history</primary>
      <secondary>by customer group</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>customer groups</primary>
      <secondary>sales history for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Sales History by Customer Group</title>
  <para>To view Sales history by Customer Group, select the "Sales History by
  Customer Group" option. The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/SA_Disp_salesHistByCustGrp.png"
                     id="Graphic542091" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption id="Caption542094">Sales History by Customer Group</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When displaying Sales history by Customer Group, you are presented
  with the following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>All Customer Groups</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847760">
        <para>Select to display Sales history for all Customer Groups.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Selected</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18477a8">
        <para>Specify Customer Group whose Sales history you want to
        display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Pattern</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18477f0">
        <para>Enter a Customer Group pattern to select a range of Customer
        Groups.</para>
        <para>Refine your search using Regular Expressions, as described in
        <xref endterm="Anchor77806" linkend="Anchor77806" />.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry role="openmfg">
      <term>All Warehouses</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847814">
        <para>Select to display Sales history by Customer Group for all
        Warehouses.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry role="openmfg">
      <term>Selected</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847838">
        <para>Specify Warehouse whose Sales history by Customer Group you want
        to display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Start Date</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847880">
        <para>Sales history by Customer Group generated on or after this date
        will be displayed.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>End Date</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18478c8">
        <para>Sales history by Customer Group generated on or before this date
        will be displayed.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Show Costs</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847910">
        <para>Select to include Costs in the display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Show Prices</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847958">
        <para>Select to include Prices in the display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Sales History</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x18479a0">
        <para>Display lists Sales history by Customer Group, using the
        specified parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>To the far right of the screen, the following buttons are
  available:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>CLOSE</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847a0c">
        <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
        desktop.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>QUERY</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847a54">
        <para>Select to generate the display, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>PRINT</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1847a9c">
        <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
